Set Words is a crossword（纵横填字） game for 2, 3 or 4 players.
The player consists of forming interlocking（环环相扣的） words,
crossword fashion, on the Set Words playing board
using letter tiles（字母片） with various score values（不同的分数值）.

Each player competes（争夺） for high score by
using their letters in combinations and locations（以组合和位置的方式） that
take best advantage of letter values and premium squares（最好地使用 字母值 与 高级方块???）
on the board.

The combined total score（综合总分） for a game
may range from about 500 points to 700 or more
depending on the skill of players.